survey_response.review_text: As of now, three consultations have taken place over there. The estimated waiting period can be 30 minutes. Dr. Jayagar Prabakaran was a nice person. But the only problem I noticed was that they consider only one week as a follow-up and after that, we have to pay the consultation fees as normal. If they can consider some concession in that, it will be really helpful.
